    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Quilts worked by the bereaved during a period of mourning, often black, white, or gray, with appropriate patterns or motifs.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
